TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PACIFIC_BRANDS_DIVISION_ID)) AS PACIFIC_BRANDS_DIVISION_ID , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PURCHASE_ORDER_NUMBER)) AS PURCHASE_ORDER_NUMBER , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PURCHASE_ORDER_SKU_LINE)) AS PURCHASE_ORDER_SKU_LINE, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PURCHASE_ORDER_LINE_STATUS)) AS PURCHASE_ORDER_LINE_STATUS, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.DESTINATION_WAREHOUSE_CODE)) AS DESTINATION_WAREHOUSE_CODE, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.STYLE)) AS STYLE, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.COLOUR)) AS COLOUR, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.DIMENSION_VAL)) AS DIMENSION_VAL, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.SIZE_NUM)) AS SIZE_NUM , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.TRANSPORT_MODE_DETAIL)) AS TRANSPORT_MODE_DETAIL, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.QUANTITY_OF_ITEM)) AS QUANTITY_OF_ITEM, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.ACTUAL_SHIP_DATE)) AS ACTUAL_SHIP_DATE, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.INTO_STORE_DATE)) AS INTO_STORE_DATE , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.REQUESTED_BY)) AS REQUESTED_BY , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.DELIVERY_TERMS)) AS DELIVERY_TERMS, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.REGION_PORT_OF_LOADING)) AS REGION_PORT_OF_LOADING, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.SUPPLIER_NUMBER)) AS SUPPLIER_NUMBER , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PRIORITY_ADVICE_DESCRIPTION)) AS PRIORITY_ADVICE_DESCRIPTION , LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.CREATE_USERID)) AS CREATE_USERID, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.PURCHASE_ORDER_AMENDMENT_NUM)) AS PURCHASE_ORDER_AMENDMENT_NUM, LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER.ORDER_CREATION_DATE)) AS ORDER_CREATION_DATE FROM STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER where CREATE_USERID ='Pac_Brands_PI_LOAD' and Create_date = (Select max(CREATE_DATE) from STG_PB_PURCHASEORDER where CREATE_USERID ='Pac_Brands_PI_LOAD' )

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
delete from EXTERNAL_PURCHASE_ORDER where as_of_date = (case when to_char(sysdate,'DAY') in ('SUNDAY','MONDAY') then (Select distinct as_of_date-7 from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) else (Select distinct as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) end) and CREATE_USERID = 'PacBrands_PI_LOAD';
commit;
